            Set mappings at variable to string_value
    Otherwise:
    Note: Use default values for common variables
    If variable = "variable_name":
            Set mappings at variable to "defaultVar"
    Otherwise if variable = "original_code":
            Set mappings at variable to "defaultVar.defaultMethod()"
    Otherwise if variable = "default_value":
            Set mappings at variable to "null"
    Otherwise if variable = "array_name":
            Set mappings at variable to "defaultArray"
    Otherwise if variable = "index":
            Set mappings at variable to "i"
    Otherwise:
            Set mappings at variable to "defaultValue"
            Return mappings

