Process called "calculate_fix_confidence" that takes strategy as FixStrategy and context as Dictionary[String, Any] returns Float:
    Note: Calculate confidence score for fix based on strategy and context
    Let base_confidence be strategy.success_probability Note: Adjust confidence based on context quality
            Let context_keys be get_dictionary_keys with dict as context
    Let context_completeness be get_list_length with list as context_keys / get_list_length with list as strategy.required_context If context_completeness > 1.0:
            Set context_completeness to 1.0 Let confidence_adjustment be context_completeness times 0.2
    Let final_confidence be base_confidence confidence_adjustment Note: Cap confidence at 1.0
    If final_confidence > 1.0:
    Set final_confidence to 1.0 Note: Minimum confidence floor
    If final_confidence < 0.1:
            Set final_confidence to 0.1 Return final_confidence

