Process called "create_calculated_performance_impact" that takes strategy as FixStrategy returns PerformanceImpact:
    Note: Calculate actual performance impact based on strategy
            Let execution_time_change be 0.0
            Let memory_usage_change be 0.0
            Let complexity_change be "unchanged"
            Let bottleneck_analysis be list containing
    Let optimization_opportunities be list containing Note: Calculate impact based on strategy type
    If strategy.strategy_type = NullCheck:
