    Add to optimization_opportunities "Use unchecked access in performance-critical loops" Otherwise if strategy.strategy_type = TypeConversion:
    Set execution_time_change to 0.005 Note: Type validation overhead
    Set memory_usage_change to 0.001 Note: Temporary objects for validation
            Set complexity_change to "increased"
