    Add to optimization_opportunities "Pre-validate types at function entry" Otherwise if strategy.strategy_type = ExceptionHandling:
    Set execution_time_change to 0.003 Note: Exception setup overhead
    Set memory_usage_change to 0.002 Note: Exception handler stack frames
            Set complexity_change to "increased"
