    Add to optimization_opportunities "Use early return patterns instead of exceptions" Otherwise if strategy.strategy_type = ResourceCleanup:
    Set execution_time_change to 0.004 Note: Cleanup operations overhead
    Set memory_usage_change to -0.001 Note: Better memory management
            Set complexity_change to "slightly_increased"
            Add to optimization_opportunities "Implement resource pooling"
    Return PerformanceImpact with:
